---
// Services Component - Research-Driven Design (2025)
//
// RESEARCH FINDINGS APPLIED:
// - Card layout best practice: title → description → feature list → CTA (Source: B2B website design 2025)
// - "Maximalist Minimalism" trend: balance white space with bold colors (Source: 2025 B2B web design trends)
// - 3-column grid for service comparison (Source: SaaS pricing page best practices)
// - Hover effects: 3D transforms, subtle glows, micro-interactions (Source: CSS hover effects 2025)
// - Strategic use of clean space for intuitive navigation (Source: B2B UX best practices)
//
// CARD STRUCTURE DECISIONS:
// - Consistent card layout creates easy comparisons for visitors
// - Gradient backgrounds (from-slate-50 to-white) provide subtle depth
// - 2xl rounded corners follow modern design standards
// - Border transitions on hover (slate-100 → brand-accent)
//
// HOVER EFFECT DECISIONS:
// - 3D lift effect: -translate-y-2 (Source: 2025 card hover trends)
// - Shadow progression: default → 2xl on hover (depth illusion)
// - Icon scale animation: 110% on card hover (subtle interaction)
// - Glow effect on cards: brand-accent shadow (lighting effect trend)
// - Arrow animation on CTA: translate-x-2 (micro-interaction)
//
// ICON DESIGN DECISIONS:
// - Gradient backgrounds (primary → accent) for visual hierarchy
// - SVG vector icons for scalability (Source: SaaS icon design best practices)
// - 8x8 icon size with 16x16 container (proper spacing ratio)
// - Consistent cyan accent color across all checkmark icons
// - White icon color for contrast against gradient backgrounds
//
// FEATURE LIST DECISIONS:
// - Checkmark icons establish trust and completion
// - Hover scale on list items for engagement (micro-interaction)
// - Consistent spacing (space-y-3) for readability
// - Text-sm size for feature items (optimal for scanning)
//
// COLOR & ACCESSIBILITY DECISIONS:
// - Brand-primary (#1E3A8A) and brand-accent (#06B6D4) maintain consistency
// - Slate-600 for body text (WCAG AA compliant contrast ratio)
// - Brand-dark for headings (maximum readability)
//
// BOTTOM CTA DECISIONS:
// - Fallback CTA for undecided visitors (reduces decision paralysis)
// - Primary button style maintains consistency with Hero
// - "Let's Talk" emphasizes consultation over hard sell
